476
00:20:59,910 --> 00:21:01,550
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
[Before and After]

477
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:03,520
See that?

478
00:21:03,690 --> 00:21:05,120
This is the first change

479
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:06,250
I'm bringing to you—

480
00:21:06,410 --> 00:21:07,870
crafting your personas.

481
00:21:06,780 --> 00:21:08,450
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
