482
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:08,560
I fe-

483
00:21:08,560 --> 00:21:10,010
I feel like I'm not even myself anymore.

484
00:21:10,010 --> 00:21:11,070
Of course it's you.

485
00:21:11,140 --> 00:21:12,600
This just brings out the side of you

486
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:13,800
that's been hidden all along.

487
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,870
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]
[Love Guide]

488
00:21:13,940 --> 00:21:16,020
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
