489
00:21:14,490 --> 00:21:14,890
Next.

490
00:21:16,930 --> 00:21:18,010
Everyone knows that

491
00:21:18,010 --> 00:21:19,730
Xuan was just a mechanic.

492
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:21,320
But through our transformation,

493
00:21:21,320 --> 00:21:23,140
he completely became

494
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:24,970
an outstanding racing driver.

495
