497
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:27,930
First impressions

498
00:21:27,140 --> 00:21:31,020
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]
[Love Guide]

499
00:21:27,930 --> 00:21:31,070
determine whether the other party
is interested in getting to know you.

500
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:32,730
[The Art of Love—
Exploring the Mysteries of Love]

501
00:21:31,410 --> 00:21:32,820
Whether you are a penniless nobody

502
00:21:32,820 --> 00:21:37,470
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]
[Love Guide]

503
00:21:33,040 --> 00:21:35,760
or a dominant alpha
that every woman longs for—

504
00:21:35,760 --> 00:21:38,040
it's all written on the persona
you present.

505
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:39,490
From that first impression,

506
00:21:39,490 --> 00:21:42,080
they judge whether the value you display

507
00:21:42,080 --> 00:21:44,520
can provide them with

508
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:46,120
enough financial security.

509
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:50,600
Never doubt our expertise.

510
00:21:50,730 --> 00:21:51,490
Here,

511
00:21:52,930 --> 00:21:54,520
I am your god—

512
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:57,010
a savior who lifts you out of

513
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:58,120
the pit of pitiful insecurity

514
00:21:58,120 --> 00:21:59,730
and helps you get back on your feet,

515
00:21:59,730 --> 00:22:01,820
a magician who transforms you from

516
00:22:02,080 --> 00:22:04,120
being ignored into

517
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,260
being universally loved.

518
00:22:13,170 --> 00:22:14,410
So far,

519
00:22:14,410 --> 00:22:16,190
the trial class worth 598 yuan is over.

520
00:22:16,190 --> 00:22:21,050
[Love Manual]

521
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:19,450
I believe you've all witnessed
the magical transformation.

522
00:22:19,450 --> 00:22:21,210
The tuition for our subsequent classes is

523
00:22:21,210 --> 00:22:22,120
3,988 yuan,

524
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:23,650
and that's where

525
00:22:23,890 --> 00:22:25,800
the real highlights begin—

526
00:22:26,040 --> 00:22:29,010
teaching you step by step
how to win a girl's heart

527
00:22:29,120 --> 00:22:29,840
and make her

528
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,880
completely obedient to you.

529
00:22:32,970 --> 00:22:33,930
-Me!
-Me!

530
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:59,080
Y-You startled me.

531
00:23:00,360 --> 00:23:01,560
Did you dye your hair?

532
00:23:03,010 --> 00:23:03,410
Wait,

533
00:23:03,800 --> 00:23:05,530
why are you here all of a sudden?

534
00:23:06,360 --> 00:23:07,420
It's Monday today.

535
00:23:08,490 --> 00:23:09,750
I took a day off in lieu.

536
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:11,730
You've been quite busy, huh?

537
00:23:11,730 --> 00:23:13,390
I haven't seen you for a while.

538
00:23:13,600 --> 00:23:14,460
Yeah. I... I...

539
00:23:14,760 --> 00:23:16,520
I-I was just...

540
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:17,250
Look,

541
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:18,800
everyone has been sent out.

542
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:20,650
I'm the only one staying behind.

543
00:23:21,730 --> 00:23:23,490
I've been busy lately,

544
00:23:23,690 --> 00:23:25,150
and I forgot to ask you out.

545
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:28,220
So busy, yet you had time
to dye your hair?

546
00:23:29,410 --> 00:23:30,470
It's not like that.

547
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:33,560
Well, the other day,

548
00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:34,080
I went

549
00:23:34,080 --> 00:23:35,140
to get a haircut, you know?

550
00:23:35,140 --> 00:23:37,750
The barber told me that

551
00:23:37,930 --> 00:23:38,990
my hair was too grey

552
00:23:39,080 --> 00:23:39,760
and didn't look good,

553
00:23:39,760 --> 00:23:41,080
and he said I should dye it.

554
00:23:41,080 --> 00:23:41,940
I-It's just...

555
00:23:42,250 --> 00:23:44,080
T-The color didn't turn out well.

556
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:45,340
Making things up, huh?

557
00:23:45,670 --> 00:23:46,280
Go on then.

558
00:23:46,970 --> 00:23:48,120
I'm not making things up.

559
00:23:48,120 --> 00:23:49,780
I'll give you another chance.

560
00:23:50,450 --> 00:23:51,310
What happened?

561
00:23:54,560 --> 00:23:55,250
Well...

562
00:23:58,700 --> 00:23:59,890
I just over-dyed it.

563
00:24:01,890 --> 00:24:04,210
Students participating in
the second phase of training,

564
00:24:04,210 --> 00:24:05,470
