00:34:53,080 --> 00:34:53,880
or owe anyone.

840
00:34:53,969 --> 00:34:55,500
Just consider me dead, too!

841
00:34:56,080 --> 00:34:56,639
Mom,

842
00:34:57,600 --> 00:34:58,720
please don't be mad.

843
00:34:58,720 --> 00:35:00,050
That's not what I meant.

844
00:35:00,810 --> 00:35:03,140
I‘ll never meddle in your business again.

845
00:35:04,850 --> 00:35:06,510
And don't call me Mom anymore.

846
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:08,120
Mom.

847
00:35:09,770 --> 00:35:10,160
Mo-

848
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:28,640
Mom,

849
00:35:29,330 --> 00:35:30,930
please don't be mad, okay?

850
00:35:30,930 --> 00:35:31,930
It's all my fault.

851
00:35:36,450 --> 00:35:37,450
When you get home,

852
00:35:37,770 --> 00:35:39,500
can you send me a WeChat message

853
00:35:39,640 --> 00:35:40,840
so I know you're safe?

854
00:36:03,890 --> 00:36:06,020
Grandma brought this here yesterday.

855
00:36:07,560 --> 00:36:08,560
Did she reply?

856
00:36:09,310 --> 00:36:10,440
Has she gotten home?

857
00:36:12,010 --> 00:36:13,040
She should have.

858
00:36:17,520 --> 00:36:18,450
Is that Grandma?

859
00:36:19,240 --> 00:36:20,100
It's my boss,

860
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:22,890
Director Lin.

861
00:36:23,330 --> 00:36:24,260
Hello, Yan Ling.

862
00:36:24,410 --> 00:36:25,420
It's urgent,

863
00:36:25,450 --> 00:36:27,310
so I'll get straight to the point.

864
00:36:27,450 --> 00:36:29,210
Are you close to that Mr. Ding

865
00:36:29,230 --> 00:36:31,160
from Oceanvision International?

866
00:36:32,290 --> 00:36:33,330
Kind of, I guess.

867
00:36:34,610 --> 00:36:36,420
He used to work for my dad.

868
00:36:36,720 --> 00:36:38,010
So you are close.

869
00:36:39,450 --> 00:36:40,640
Here's the situation.

870
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:41,450
President Sun

871
00:36:41,470 --> 00:36:43,040
just had a meeting with them.

872
00:36:43,040 --> 00:36:44,120
Since your name wasn't on

873
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:46,160
the list the review committee
submitted to them,

874
00:36:46,160 --> 00:36:47,340
they suddenly changed their mind

875
00:36:47,340 --> 00:36:49,400
and said they'd cancel the donation.

876
00:36:49,850 --> 00:36:50,620
Is that so?

877
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:52,970
That's over 10 million in real cash—

878
00:36:52,970 --> 00:36:54,190
it's not a small sum.

879
00:36:54,490 --> 00:36:55,720
After President Sun came back,

880
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:57,850
he called a meeting
with the relevant staff.

881
00:36:57,850 --> 00:36:59,660
In the end, everyone agreed

882
00:36:59,930 --> 00:37:00,640
that

883
00:37:00,640 --> 00:37:02,440
you should represent our school

884
00:37:02,810 --> 00:37:04,330
and go talk to Mr. Ding,

885
00:37:04,330 --> 00:37:05,240
to see why they

886
00:37:05,240 --> 00:37:06,500
decided not to donate.

887
00:37:07,850 --> 00:37:08,290
Hello?

888
00:37:09,080 --> 00:37:10,880
Ms. Yan, are you listening to me?

889
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:12,380
I'm listening.

890
00:37:13,560 --> 00:37:14,560
Looking at it now,

891
00:37:14,770 --> 00:37:15,290
Mr. Ding's choice

892
00:37:15,290 --> 00:37:16,290
of our school,

893
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:17,410
especially our department,

894
00:37:17,410 --> 00:37:18,820
had a lot to do with

895
00:37:19,080 --> 00:37:20,040
you being here.

896
00:37:20,680 --> 00:37:21,250
So,

897
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:22,570
the school and I

898
00:37:22,720 --> 00:37:24,920
hope you can put aside personal grudges

899
00:37:24,930 --> 00:37:26,880
and think more about
the school and the students.

900
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:29,330
I don't have any grudges
against our school.

901
00:37:29,330 --> 00:37:29,970
All the better

902
00:37:29,970 --> 00:37:31,410
then.

903
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:33,240
Please go have a proper talk with him

904
00:37:33,240 --> 00:37:34,560
and try to persuade him.

905
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:35,490
This scholarship

906
00:37:35,490 --> 00:37:38,370
will prioritize
students with financial difficulties.

907
00:37:38,370 --> 00:37:39,080
Yan Ling,

908
00:37:39,080 --> 00:37:41,320
make sure to convey our sincerity

909
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:44,700
and do a good job persuading him
on behalf of the school.

910
00:37:45,850 --> 00:37:47,380
No. 3 of the Five-Step Trap:

911
00:37:47,450 --> 00:37:49,640
Pit No. 3, the Lure Trap.

912
00:37:49,970 --> 00:37:52,850
When you've successfully attracted
your prey

913
00:37:52,850 --> 00:37:54,720
with Curiosity Trap and Obsession Trap,

914
00:37:54,720 --> 00:37:55,330
it's time

915
00:37:55,330 --> 00:37:58,080
to lead her into Pit No. 3, the Lure Trap.

916
00:37:58,160 --> 00:38:01,440
A skilled hunter doesn't actively
chase the prey,

917
00:38:01,680 --> 00:38:04,720
but makes the prey actively
follow your demands,

918
00:38:04,720 --> 00:38:05,850
follow your rhythm,

919
00:38:05,850 --> 00:38:07,520
and obey your words, until...

920
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:12,050
They fall right into the trap themselves.

921
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:14,980
I ordered your favorite
home-style braised yellow croaker.

922
00:38:14,980 --> 00:38:16,040
I didn't ask you out

923
00:38:17,010 --> 00:38:18,330
to eat.

924
00:38:18,330 --> 00:38:19,490
The yellow croaker here

925
00:38:19,490 --> 00:38:20,620
is all wild-caught.

926
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:22,410
When I heard you wanted to see me,

927
00:38:22,410 --> 00:38:25,080
-I thought this place is the most suitable...
-I've said

928
00:38:25,080 --> 00:38:25,940
I'm not eating.

929
00:38:28,370 --> 00:38:29,680
Do your words count?

930
00:38:30,850 --> 00:38:31,520
You asked me

931
00:38:32,010 --> 00:38:33,640
to stay out of your life

932
00:38:33,640 --> 00:38:34,650
and not bother you anymore.

933
00:38:34,650 --> 00:38:35,930
I did it.

934
00:38:36,680 --> 00:38:38,120
But you are still not happy.

935
00:38:38,120 --> 00:38:40,380
You canceled the scholarship on purpose

936
00:38:41,230 --> 00:38:42,960
just to make me come and beg you.

937
00:38:45,450 --> 00:38:47,580
I never expected you'd see me this way.

938
00:38:48,330 --> 00:38:48,890
Ling,

939
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:51,850
how did we end up like this?

940
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:58,550
Actually, this restaurant

941
00:38:58,550 --> 00:39:01,480
is most famous for its
osmanthus chestnut ice cream.

942
00:39:02,290 --> 00:39:04,090
But I know you don't eat dessert.

943
00:39:06,640 --> 00:39:09,240
You see, I keep everything about you
in my mind.

944
00:39:10,770 --> 00:39:12,500
You're supposed to do the same.

945
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:16,140
It was me who stayed with you
through the hardest times.

946
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:19,120
We will always be

947
00:39:20,240 --> 00:39:22,100
the closest people in this world.

948
00:39:28,240 --> 00:39:29,900
Fish maw and old chicken soup.

949
00:39:30,640 --> 00:39:31,970
It's full of collagen.

950
00:39:32,890 --> 00:39:34,420
It's the best for you girls.

951
00:39:34,680 --> 00:39:36,280
Here, eat it while it's warm.

952
00:39:40,680 --> 00:39:41,200
What,

953
00:39:41,640 --> 00:39:42,290
do you want me

954
00:39:42,290 --> 00:39:45,020
to coax you into eating
like when you were little?

955
00:39:47,970 --> 00:39:49,230
Come on, be a good girl.

956
00:39:50,160 --> 00:39:51,120
You need to eat well.

957
00:39:51,120 --> 00:39:53,240
Only after you've eaten enough
can you grow strong,

958
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:54,190
and then...

959
00:39:59,720 --> 00:40:00,780
Is this necessary?

960
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:03,470
It's just a meal.

961
00:40:03,930 --> 00:40:05,990
As if I'm going to do something to you.

962
00:40:06,970 --> 00:40:08,040
Your mom carried bags of stuff

963
00:40:08,040 --> 00:40:09,500
to visit me in the hospital

964
00:40:09,530 --> 00:40:11,530
and beg me to help you no matter what.

965
00:40:11,720 --> 00:40:13,980
And you're the one who asked me out today.

966
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:15,810
Just give me a straight answer.

967
00:40:15,810 --> 00:40:18,340
Do you want me to donate
that 10 million or not?

968
00:40:20,490 --> 00:40:21,640
It's the school that wants it.

969
00:40:21,640 --> 00:40:23,300
I don't care about the school.

970
00:40:23,370 --> 00:40:25,260
If you say it, I'll donate.

971
00:40:31,060 --> 00:40:32,330
Say it.

972
00:40:35,490 --> 00:40:37,220
Say that it's you who want this,

973
00:40:38,520 --> 00:40:40,050
that it's what you wish for.

974
00:41:02,040 --> 00:41:02,890
Say it.

975
00:41:03,890 --> 00:41:06,170
Say that it's you who want you to do this,

976
00:41:06,970 --> 00:41:08,500
that it's what you wish for.

977
00:41:08,750 --> 00:41:09,260
This...

978
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:10,440
It's me who

979
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:12,120
want you to do this.

980
00:41:14,850 --> 00:41:16,560
This is what I wish for.

981
00:41:20,100 --> 00:41:24,850
[The Dark Romance]

982
00:41:30,930 --> 00:41:31,630
Let me do it, sister-in-law.

983
00:41:31,630 --> 00:41:32,060
Let me.

984
00:41:33,120 --> 00:41:34,320
Sorry to trouble you.

985
00:41:35,680 --> 00:41:36,010
Here.

986
00:41:39,240 --> 00:41:40,560
Please take good care of Ling.

987
00:41:40,560 --> 00:41:41,360
Get in the car.

988
00:41:45,450 --> 00:41:45,910
Come on.

989
00:41:47,080 --> 00:41:48,140
Go ahead and get in.

990
00:41:48,410 --> 00:41:49,160
Listen to your uncle.
